---
//SVG
import PlusIcon from '@svgs/plus.svg'
---

<!-- FAQ -->
<section class="px-page py-section-lg">
  <div class="contained">
    <div class="gap-gutter grid md:grid-cols-12">
      <div data-animate class="md:col-span-5">
        <div class="top-section-lg sticky">
          <h2 class="text-title-md mb-el-sm font-semibold">FAQs</h2>
          <p class="text-body-md text-dark-1">
            Our team of certified experts is ready to provide you with the most
            detailed property report in the state.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div data-animate-stagger class="md:col-span-7">
        <details class="group border-light-4 py-el-xl border-b first:border-t">
          <summary
            class="gap-el-xl flex cursor-pointer list-none items-center [&::-webkit-details-marker]:hidden"
          >
            <div
              class="flex size-10 shrink-0 items-center justify-center rounded-full bg-[#FEE6D7] transition-colors group-open:bg-[#FECCAF]"
            >
              <PlusIcon
                class="size-6 transition-transform duration-200 group-open:rotate-45"
              />
            </div>
            <span class="text-body-lg font-medium"
              >How much does a home inspection cost?</span
            >
          </summary>
          <p
            class="mt-el-lg text-body-md text-dark-1"
            style="padding-left: calc(2.5rem + var(--spacing-el-xl))"
          >
            Typically between $300 and $500, depending on the size and age of
            the home. We provide transparent, flat-rate pricing with no hidden
            fees.
          </p>
        </details>
        <details class="group border-light-4 py-el-xl border-b">
          <summary
            class="gap-el-xl flex cursor-pointer list-none items-center [&::-webkit-details-marker]:hidden"
          >
            <div
              class="flex size-10 shrink-0 items-center justify-center rounded-full bg-[#FEE6D7] transition-colors group-open:bg-[#FECCAF]"
            >
              <PlusIcon
                class="size-6 transition-transform duration-200 group-open:rotate-45"
              />
            </div>
            <span class="text-body-lg font-medium"
              >Who hires the home inspector?</span
            >
          </summary>
          <p
            class="mt-el-lg text-body-md text-dark-1"
            style="padding-left: calc(2.5rem + var(--spacing-el-xl))"
          >
            Typically the buyer of the home chooses and hires the home
            inspector. There are occasions that the seller has a pre-listing
            inspection done, though this is rare.
          </p>
        </details>
        <details class="group border-light-4 py-el-xl border-b">
          <summary
            class="gap-el-xl flex cursor-pointer list-none items-center [&::-webkit-details-marker]:hidden"
          >
            <div
              class="flex size-10 shrink-0 items-center justify-center rounded-full bg-[#FEE6D7] transition-colors group-open:bg-[#FECCAF]"
            >
              <PlusIcon
                class="size-6 transition-transform duration-200 group-open:rotate-45"
              />
            </div>
            <span class="text-body-lg font-medium"
              >How long does a home inspection take?</span
            >
          </summary>
          <p
            class="mt-el-lg text-body-md text-dark-1"
            style="padding-left: calc(2.5rem + var(--spacing-el-xl))"
          >
            Most inspections take between 2 and 4 hours. Larger or older homes
            may take longer. You'll receive your full digital report within 24
            hours of completion.
          </p>
        </details>
        <details class="group border-light-4 py-el-xl border-b">
          <summary
            class="gap-el-xl flex cursor-pointer list-none items-center [&::-webkit-details-marker]:hidden"
          >
            <div
              class="flex size-10 shrink-0 items-center justify-center rounded-full bg-[#FEE6D7] transition-colors group-open:bg-[#FECCAF]"
            >
              <PlusIcon
                class="size-6 transition-transform duration-200 group-open:rotate-45"
              />
            </div>
            <span class="text-body-lg font-medium"
              >Should I be present during the inspection?</span
            >
          </summary>
          <p
            class="mt-el-lg text-body-md text-dark-1"
            style="padding-left: calc(2.5rem + var(--spacing-el-xl))"
          >
            We strongly encourage it. Being present allows you to ask questions
            in real time and get a firsthand understanding of the property's
            condition from our inspector.
          </p>
        </details>
        <details class="group border-light-4 py-el-xl border-b">
          <summary
            class="gap-el-xl flex cursor-pointer list-none items-center [&::-webkit-details-marker]:hidden"
          >
            <div
              class="flex size-10 shrink-0 items-center justify-center rounded-full bg-[#FEE6D7] transition-colors group-open:bg-[#FECCAF]"
            >
              <PlusIcon
                class="size-6 transition-transform duration-200 group-open:rotate-45"
              />
            </div>
            <span class="text-body-lg font-medium"
              >What does a home inspection include?</span
            >
          </summary>
          <p
            class="mt-el-lg text-body-md text-dark-1"
            style="padding-left: calc(2.5rem + var(--spacing-el-xl))"
          >
            We inspect all major systems including the roof, foundation, HVAC,
            plumbing, electrical, and more. Our standard inspection includes
            thermal imaging and moisture detection at no extra cost.
          </p>
        </details>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
